  26,207,"((How) that wherewith) Allah's punishment (they were contented) because of the reprieve (naught availeth them) from Allah's punishment?"
  26,210,"(The devils) at the time of the Prophet (pbuh) (did not bring it down) did not bring the Qur'an down."
  26,212,"(Lo! verily they) i.e. the devils (are banished from the hearing) they are prevented from hearing the revelation."
  26,215,"(And lower thy wing (in kindness) unto those believers who follow thee) be kind to the believers."
  26,221,"(Shall I inform you upon whom the devils descend) with fortune telling?"
